    "feature_note": "Bridge built WITH the d3d12-recording-shim feature: the tonemap real-pass arm routes through the linked recording shim, so arming RXGD_CAP_TONEMAP_REAL_PASS can make rxgd_record_pass return RXGD_STATUS_OK only after a real recorded dispatch. The shipping feature-off bridge still fails closed with real_dispatch_path_not_linked. target/debug/rurix_godot.dll is a mutable build artifact."
